  "title": "月のテンペスト 05 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "garden-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……部屋にこもってずっと勉強してたから\n夜風が気持ちいいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… I've been cooped up in my room studying this whole time‚\nthe night breeze feels nice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8666666667,
      "endTime": 9.8834692637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "勉強してたかな？\nずっとお喋りしてた気もするけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Studying?\nI feel like we just kept chatting the whole time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1168031692,
      "endTime": 15.6351249694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "もう、意地悪言わないで\n気分転換が終わったら、ちゃんと勉強するから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "정말‚ 심술부리지 마\nI'll study properly after I've cleared my head.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4,
      "endTime": 23.831882286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……そういえば、高校受験の時も\nこうやって二人で試験勉強したわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ even when we were studying for high school entrance exams‚\nwe studied together like this‚ didn't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.0185489336,
      "endTime": 30.308548704699998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は琴乃ちゃん、凄く勉強頑張ったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You worked so hard studying back then‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5018818854,
      "endTime": 34.6440587996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "渚と同じ高校に行くって約束したから……\n約束を守るために必死に頑張ったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because I promised you I'd go to the same high school‚ Nagisa…\nI worked desperately to keep that promise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.8440588473,
      "endTime": 41.9560314654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "入学式の日に琴乃ちゃんが「アイドルになる」って\n私に宣言して……あれはびっくりしたなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On the day of the entrance ceremony‚ you said \"I'm going to become an idol\"\nand declared it to me… I was really surprised then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1493648368,
      "endTime": 51.2056438286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんはアイドルが嫌いだと思ってたから\n意外だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you hated idols‚ Kotono‚\nso it was a surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3923103808,
      "endTime": 55.9678884027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりで驚いたわよね\nでも、私はずっと前から考えていたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was sudden and surprised you‚ didn't it?\nBut‚ I had been thinking about it for a long time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1545550981,
      "endTime": 63.548614088600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "いつからアイドルになろうと思ってたの？　私と一緒に\n麻奈さんのライブDVDを見たのがきっかけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since when have you been thinking about becoming an idol? Was it after you watched\nMana-san's live DVD together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7552808124,
      "endTime": 71.051697858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "それもあるけど、一番のきっかけは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was part of it‚ but the biggest reason was…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2450311342,
      "endTime": 75.7739654222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――長瀬麻奈の事故から数ヶ月後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few months after Mana Nagase's accident",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7872987746,
      "endTime": 78.22063150390001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 78.2206315039
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 78.2206315039
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "形見分け……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Dividing keepsakes…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1206331252,
      "endTime": 80.6829007148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "琴乃の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "琴乃の母",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktnmam001.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ麻奈の部屋の物を処分しようと思って……\nだから、ほしい物があれば今のうちに持って行きなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking of cleaning out Mana's room soon…\nSo‚ if there's anything you want‚ take it now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8695673624,
      "endTime": 89.85623480480001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.069567871
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "……そうよね。お姉ちゃんの部屋\nいつまでもこのままにしておけないもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……that's right. My sister's room\nI can't leave it like this forever‚ can I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.069567871,
      "endTime": 98.07512331000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.2817897478
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、お姉ちゃんの持ち物で）\n（私が取っておきたい物ってなんだろう？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But‚ among my sister's belongings‚）\n（what is it that I want to keep?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2817897478,
      "endTime": 106.0954859415,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 20158.21025219999,
          "startTime": 118.44
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.2954848288
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "これと、これと……結構いろんな物があるわね\nあら？　これは……手帳？　スケジュール帳かしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This and this… There are quite a few things here.\nHuh? This is… a notebook? Is it a planner?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3288186708,
      "endTime": 125.604238669,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17637.84799589999,
          "startTime": 125.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 125.8042384783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "中に何か書いてある……ええと……\n「今日も琴乃は私が歌うことを認めてくれなかった」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something's written inside… Let's see…\n\"Today too‚ Kotono wouldn't acknowledge my singing.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8042384783,
      "endTime": 140.0624475162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.2957804362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_06-mna022.m4a",
      "text": "（今日も琴乃は私が歌うことを認めてくれなかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Today too‚ Kotono wouldn't acknowledge my singing.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.2957880656,
      "endTime": 145.9125815073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_06-mna023.m4a",
      "text": "（お客さんは一杯入ってくれている）\n（でも新人の私は毎日ミスの連続でヘコんじゃう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The audience was packed）\n（But as a newbie‚ I keep making mistakes every day and I'm so down）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.1192480404,
      "endTime": 153.6780886014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 153.9693820316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_06-mna024.m4a",
      "text": "（{user}くんや三枝さんはいつも笑って）\n（フォローしてくれるけど、悪いな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But {user} and Saegusa-san always smile）\n（and support me‚ but I feel bad…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.9693820316,
      "endTime": 158.4195342379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_06-mna025.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃に寂しい思いをさせて、みんなに迷惑かけて……）\n（私、全然ダメだ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'm making Kotono lonely‚ and I'm bothering everyone…）\n（I'm no good at all…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.7461986222,
      "endTime": 165.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 166.0163337069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_06-mna026.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、私は――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But‚ I--）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.0163337069,
      "endTime": 168.4666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mnaroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "mnaroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 169.6666392007
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "これ、手帳じゃない……お姉ちゃんの日記だ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn't a planner… It's my sister's diary…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.7064716813,
      "endTime": 176.1278324601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "garden-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 177.3411576268
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
