    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "私もそう思う。それに、私達がステージに立つ理由は\nスリクスに見せつけるためじゃない……そうでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think so too. Besides‚ the reason why we stand on stage\nisn't to show off to ⅢX… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 388.3910279826,
      "endTime": 398.5678084925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "garden-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 399.8144509868
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "私が大事にしたいのは、今はもう――\n琴乃ちゃんだけじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I want to treasure‚ is now no longer just\nKotono alone",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 400.8477919495,
      "endTime": 408.9206491387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "私は、私達は、四人で頑張って……\n琴乃ちゃんがいつでも戻れるようにしておくから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ we‚ will do our best with these four people…\nWe'll make sure that you can come back anytime‚ Kotono‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 409.1339823957,
      "endTime": 418.9013972517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "だから私――琴乃ちゃんとは一緒に行けない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I-I can't go with you‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 419.1147304133,
      "endTime": 425.5223496989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 426.6890087839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "ふざけないでよ！！\n月ストは、琴乃ちゃんが思ってるほど弱くなんかない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stop messing around!!\nMoon Tempest isn't as weak as you think‚ Kotono!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 427.7223497466,
      "endTime": 435.2110117988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 436.4176624692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "――琴乃ちゃん、おかえりなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Kotono‚ welcome back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 437.4510034319,
      "endTime": 440.5954932448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn033.m4a",
      "text": "（私が辛い時は支えてくれて、立ち止まった時は背中を）\n（押してくれる。渚と一緒なら私はこれからも――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（You support me when I'm having a hard time‚ and push me in the back when I stop moving forward.）\n（With you‚ Nagisa‚ I can keep going--）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 440.7954933402,
      "endTime": 453.18635466070003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "garden-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 454.4196640886
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn034.m4a",
      "text": "最初は、アイドルってなんなのか……お姉ちゃんが\nどうして夢中で頑張ってたのか分からなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ I didn't know what it meant to be an idol… or why my sister\nwas working so hard with such passion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 455.4530050513,
      "endTime": 464.3679256674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn035.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今ならお姉ちゃんの気持ちが分かる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ I understand how my sister felt.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 464.5745924867,
      "endTime": 468.5279938615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn036.m4a",
      "text": "私もお姉ちゃんに負けないくらい\nアイドルが好きになったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because I‚ too‚ have come to love\nbeing an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 468.7346604423,
      "endTime": 473.46291456980003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ。それじゃあ、麻奈さんに負けないくらい\nアイドルを好きになった琴乃ちゃんの、今の夢は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. In that case‚ what's your dream now‚ Kotono? One that makes you love\nbeing an idol as much as Mana-san did?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 473.6762478269,
      "endTime": 482.3369732297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn037.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんなとアイドルの頂点に立つこと\nお姉ちゃんも届かなかった、アイドルの頂点に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's to stand at the top as idols together with everyone in Moon Tempest.\nTo the top as idols‚ a place even my sister couldn't reach…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 482.536973039,
      "endTime": 490.9772222913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn038.m4a",
      "text": "きっと今まで以上に大変なことが沢山あるけど……\n渚、これからも私と一緒に進んでくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure there will be many more difficult things than there have been until now…\nNagisa‚ will you continue to move forward with me from now on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 491.1905556437,
      "endTime": 502.77729022479997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "うん、もちろん。私もアイドルが好きだから\n琴乃ちゃんと一緒にアイドルの頂点に立ちたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ of course. Because I like being an idol too‚\nI want to stand at the top as idols together with you‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 502.963956777,
      "endTime": 512.3923013129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_05-ktn039.m4a",
      "text": "行きましょう、二人で……みんなで……\n青春全部かけて、アイドルの最高峰へ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's go‚ just the two of us… with everyone…\nPutting our entire youth on the line‚ to the highest peak of idolhood!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 512.5856343982,
      "endTime": 522.1421422716,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
